                A high intensity trainings aimed towards people with little or no experience in order to put them on
                the path of becoming true professionals.
            </p>
        </b-benefit>

        <b-benefit>
            <b-heading>
                <SignpostIcon/>
                <h3>Onboarding Programs</h3>
            </b-heading>
