                increase efficiency, engagement and retention.
            </p>
        </b-benefit>

        <b-benefit>
            <b-heading>
                <BooksIcon/>
                <h3>Educational Curriculums</h3>
            </b-heading>
            <p>
                A handcrafted syllabus and training materials with the goal of improving certain skills over a long
                period of time.
            </p>
        </b-benefit>

        <b-benefit>
            <b-heading>
                <NurtureIcon/>
                <h3>Mentorship</h3>
            </b-heading>
